main event: A UFO sighting was reported in Lincoln, Nebraska on July 11, 1959.
interesting points: The observation was a ground-visual type,No detailed information on the object or its course was provided,The film showing the UFO had been lost from the file,The sighting was connected to a subsequent event involving a Northwestern Airlines accident,The phenomenon observed might have been reflections rather than an actual UFO.
witness description: The witness took an 8mm film of the sighting under bright sunlight.
